From 06c4c5d8c876ef50016dd679f94bb46d5c0af44c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: BiteDash Build Fix <joseph@bitedash.co.zw>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 04:45:02 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Add live GPS tracking and Paynow admin credentials screen

GPS tracking (LocationTrackingService.kt):
- New foreground service using FusedLocationProviderClient
- Sends driver lat/lng to Firestore every 10 seconds
- Starts automatically when driver accepts a delivery
- Stops automatically when driver marks delivery complete
- Shows persistent notification while tracking is active

AndroidManifest.xml:
- Added ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION, ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION
- Added FOREGROUND_SERVICE, FOREGROUND_SERVICE_LOCATION
- Added POST_NOTIFICATIONS, INTERNET permissions
- Declared LocationTrackingService with foregroundServiceType=location

DriverOrdersScreen.kt:
- Accept delivery now starts GPS via startForegroundService()
- Complete delivery now stops GPS service
- Driver ID passed automatically from viewmodel

DriverDeliveryViewModel.kt:
- driverId made public (val) so screen can pass it to the service

BiteDashViewModel.kt:
- Added savePaynowCredentials() - writes Integration ID and Key
  to Firestore admin_settings document securely

BiteDashMainApp.kt:
- Added Paynow tab (tab 3) to admin portal TabRow
- Added PaynowSettingsTab composable: fields for Integration ID
  and Integration Key with show/hide toggle, save button,
  confirmation message, and security notes
- Credentials only visible to admin-role Firebase users
- Added missing imports: verticalScroll, Visibility icons,
  PasswordVisualTransformation

build.gradle.kts:
- Uncommented play-services-location dependency (required for GPS)
